These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, monopoly, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, martial-arts, mystery
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer, mechanic, security-guard
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the dressmaker is on the right of the mechanic##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 7. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
10. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person playing go##1
12. the person playing chess is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person watching mystery movies##2
13. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the person playing poker is the owner of the hamster##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
16. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
17. the dressmaker is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Game    | poker   | chess            | go | monopoly        |
| Movie-Genre        | musical       | martial-arts         | mystery     | crime       |
| Hobby       | hiking     | drawing        | puzzles     | magic-tricks |
| Job         | lawyer     | security-guard | mechanic    | dressmaker   |
| Pet         | hamster    | lizard         | bird        | frog         |
| Sport       | surfing    | baseball       | lacrosse    | handball     |
| Transport   | helicopter | snowmobile     | car         | bike         |

