 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the liverpoolcher is the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person who growslily is between the mexican and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
10. the chef is on the left of the nurse##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
